reviewText: On this DVD, we expected to see Fluffy most of the time, but it didn't work out that way. He's mostly the host of this show, and other comedians do the stand up, with one or two short spotlights for Fluffy. The guest comics used some language and adult comedy, so this one isn't suitable for family viewing. Adults would like it fine. Item arrived in excellent shape, and shipping was fast. Would recommend seller and would buy from again. A+
Title: Gabriel Iglesias Presents: Stand-Up Revolution - Season Two

reviewText: This one is Not anyware near as good as the first one.There where not as many comedians as on the first one, on the first one I could not wait to play it again, the second one it took alot to play it again.  mainly because they spent so much time patting them selves on the back, that it left no time for real comedyIf they make a third one, I HOPE ITS BETTER THAN THIS ONEthe only reason this sold, was because the first one was real good
summary: Not anyware near as good as the first one
Title: Gabriel Iglesias Presents: Stand-Up Revolution - Season Two

reviewText: Hope there wil be a third season or cartoon down the road. If you like his stand-up, you will like this.
Title: Gabriel Iglesias Presents: Stand-Up Revolution - Season Two

reviewText: It seems like they spent a lot of time on other projects on this one, and gave less time to the comedians to perform. I like this show, but I want to see more of the comedians, and not as much other stuff.
summary: Not too shabby, but could have been better
Title: Gabriel Iglesias Presents: Stand-Up Revolution - Season Two

reviewText: Absolutely love Gabriel. Most of the other comedians are good too. Do wish there would be more of Gabriel on the show. Worth the watch though.
